<SYNC Start=6655018><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=6655050><P Class=KRCC>
ends here in the<br>
Capitol of Alabama
<SYNC Start=6658186><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=6658218><P Class=KRCC>
