<SYNC Start=6672107><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=6673418><P Class=KRCC>
But with our commitment,
<SYNC Start=6675146><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=6675177><P Class=KRCC>
