<SYNC Start=6682474><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=6682506><P Class=KRCC>
(CROWD CHEERING)
<SYNC Start=6684842><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=6684873><P Class=KRCC>
And we embrace<br>
this new energy so boldly,
<SYNC Start=6688010><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=6688042><P Class=KRCC>
embody it so fervently,
<SYNC Start=6690570><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
