illuminates a great darkness.
<SYNC Start=6693291><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=6693802><P Class=KRCC>
(CHEERING)
<SYNC Start=6695051><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=6696394><P Class=KRCC>
Our society<br>
has distorted who we are.
<SYNC Start=6699147><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=6700714><P Class=KRCC>
From slavery<br>
to the Reconstruction
<SYNC Start=6703306><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
