<SYNC Start=6743563><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=6744393><P Class=KRCC>
But we know the truth.
<SYNC Start=6745450><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=6746986><P Class=KRCC>
