<SYNC Start=6770795><P Class=KRCC>
(CHEERING)
<SYNC Start=6772074><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=6772106><P Class=KRCC>
No man, no myth,
<SYNC Start=6775243><P Class=KRCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=6776298><P Class=KRCC>
